Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.68,0:00:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高智能方程式 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的溫柔體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支持著我折斷受傷的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被稱為「愛」的繃帶所保護
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不回頭 奮勇向前的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那種勇氣經常是你給我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望的風灼熱地燃燒起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.48,0:00:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送來極度興奮的熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果到達你那裡 我想告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.16,0:01:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已不用再猶疑 我答應過你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not strong but my wind is high
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我並不孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.45,0:01:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為明天便在面前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我信賴的力量並沒有減退
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預感的風在心坎裡飛舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以再次起飛的心跳已經回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.08,0:02:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓你看看那天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在已是去到哪裡也不感害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not strong but my wind is high
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ROUND 3.「再上征途」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.24,0:02:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想起當日的事 我的身體現在也會發抖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令媽媽和明日香那樣傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的想過不再賽車了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經打算放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.43,0:02:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能忘記賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想歸隊 修哥我想參賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那個極限領域的陰影困擾著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能參賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會克服給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不能參賽我會更痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很勇敢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但正如你所知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的SUGO已經沒法容納你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車隊招攬了安尼·古利特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是他要取得好成績的重要關頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為車隊的管理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在不可以出手幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你故意為難他呢 修
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是ASURADA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒決定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這把車匙的跑車
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會認同隼人以外的車手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:03:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在菅生正準備一隊二線車隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們收購了在上季退出的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,THEODOLITE車隊的參賽權
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,THEODOLITE…是安尼的舊車隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我受不了，被AOI車隊洋洋得意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 古莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在的確正籌備二線車隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事先聲明 資金方面很緊迫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設備和人手亦很缺乏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那裡的確還有一個空缺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.30,0:04:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我加入 我求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但首席車手始終是古利特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使ASURADA曾奪取冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它仍是去年的機件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但修他一直都在等你回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說為了你祇須要保留空缺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車隊的名稱是「SUGO WINNERS」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經在六號車房裡準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到他和明日香的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心情就複雜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視網膜確認
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請隨便說些話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ASURADA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲紋核對正確
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是登記了的車手風見隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 ASURADA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遺棄了你這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的外觀看來有點改變
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有發生甚麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座位有點不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,THANK YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的狀態怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我曾一度失去大部份機件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在已經重新尋回
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連唯一的車手也回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一切都恢復正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 ASURADA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰擅自坐在我的跑車裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣做令我很頭痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美樹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介 還有良平
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才修…不 領隊告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SUGO WINNERS的車手已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的曾經打算引退後 轉為經營修理工場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們三個來來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諷不能就此放棄ASURADA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並說盡量想辦沃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然車身部份和電腦的一半曾損毀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但幸好有記憶留下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然修理它是很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我有點不順意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而當我聽到隼人你想再次參賽時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同樣有點不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你和ASURADA分手時受了重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長一直堅信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人一定會歸隊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良平
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之這樣我們又能角逐冠軍了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開心到激動呼丁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而明日香那種獨特的廚藝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很懷念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是曾答應我會退出比賽的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想聽你的狡辯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾多次想告訴妳我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼啊 那麼你對我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想和我一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我求婚的算甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想妳一直在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和妳訂婚的心意是沒有變的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎樣也不能退出比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會原諒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再管你的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽也好做甚麼都好 隨便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「法國 洛曼賽道」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱身圈開始前30分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在風見隼人選手的車隊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SUGO WINNERS的閘門升起了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲夢般的意外後整整一年后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩屆冠軍車手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:11:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在精神奕奕地在賽道出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光榮地復出參加格蘭披治
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是意想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二線車隊竟然用那麼舊的跑車
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SUGO也真有膿量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覓敢看不起格蘭披治
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城之內小姐覓然也認為
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那車隊較我們好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拋棄了呢 新條
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見隼人比你優秀嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨！武士小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古迪里昂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你已經完全康復呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見 恭喜你復出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 哈利先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以那麼輕鬆恭喜他嗎 哈利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人的復出對你來說是大災難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就姑且不論
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你的排名一定會下跌一位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下跌排名的衹是你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊 你這個拖後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你追傢伙 誰是拖後腿！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你是第一次出任領隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你帶了個不容忽視的傢伙回來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菅生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個領隊也真有辦沃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚麼也沒做過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是隼人自己的順望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾以為今季還是AOI的天下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣後半段的賽事就精彩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看下去才知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為隼人有段空白期
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾你們談話真對不起 領隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科特蘭小姐有事找你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 麻煩你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 保捷賀爾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 安尼 狀態怎樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀態不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見隼人由今場比賽開始復出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得很緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼？你是風見的車迷嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和我年紀相近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是歷史上第一個兩屆冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個偉大的前輩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到嗎 菅生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和風見初出道時很不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彬彬有禮 很有前途啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱身圈開始前20分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪了 安尼 比賽時再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又若無其事的回來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香一定很生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒指…她還給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也估計到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香也很可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要她原諒我太自私了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香可能不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追是你自己決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你要答應我一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再接觸ZERO領域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追是甚麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是人類能踏進的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要意氣用事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是要回來戰勝那個領域的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要自大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你所想般簡單的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.14,0:14:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之如果你不想在17歲時英年早逝的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不要接觸那個領域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:14:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法國格蘭披治預賽預選 最後一組衹剩下5分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在賽道上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SUGO WINNERS的風見隼人和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外四部車正全力衝刺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行最後一次的排位賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AsURADA 改變齒輪比
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由三速改為五速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升高定風翼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再升高的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在四個彎角時會不能達到最大馬力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後風見隼人在3分06秒內完成預賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但排位沒改變仍然是第八位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在直路盡頭的極速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和AOI的仍有20公里的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的引擎是去年那一款
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以隼人已經做得很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.11,0:15:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 美樹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在明天前會再想辦沃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧提起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你還能在預賽進入前8名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是甚麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我衹是覺得自己很沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來參賽卻令明日香哭得那麼傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在仍然不肯接聽電話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不可以被這種事分神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要明日香明白我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就一定要努力比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香一定會明白你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著是體育消息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們送上CYBER FORMULA
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法國格蘭披治預賽第二天的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是菅生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你在訊競聲後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出你的姓名和有甚麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.77,0:18:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是純子嬸嬸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的不在家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳在家的話 我求求妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以接聽我的電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嬸嬸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 明日香 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我衹是打電話給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其實想立即去妳那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用介意 嬸嬸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我說甚麼也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個媽媽真的太沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很清楚隼人做錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他始終…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望妳原諒他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望妳明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那樣做是為了消除煩腦和痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嬸嬸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我―他約覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:19:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人還是會復出參賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…他一聲不響地就決定那樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們曾說過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何事也要一起面對的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「法國格蘭披治 決賽」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抵消馬力的差距 你就要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用升壓渦和轉直路前的彎角
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不敢說足夠 但已經盡力而為了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀態怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家盡力的結果一會就能看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人生氣說我衹顧工作而沒介紹你給他認識
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是安尼·古利特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還是第二年參賽但進步很快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 領隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不可以說是隊友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家同是SUGO的車手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要融洽相處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是很緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:20:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覓然可以和風見前輩一起比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見前輩是我的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麼事 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你那時死了就好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你就可以名留青史了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有3分鐘開始比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.75,0:20:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維修站人員請離開賽道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉入第一彎角的是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.87,0:20:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排頭位的布林多·加賀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著是安尼·古利特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而風見隼人亦以巧妙的起步越過日吉進佔第七位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在追個圈決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！ASURADA
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:20:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼空白時期了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.22,0:21:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 風見越過保捷賀爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但MISSION利用氣流前進正緊貼ASURADA11
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他預測到這個彎角嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別阻攔我 古迪里昂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和哈利玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條 你打算在那裡玩到何時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 我不會給你過頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條還未使用最好的調較
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要繼續這樣給他施壓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是風見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ASURADA終於迫近第四、五位的車了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在直路無論如何會被追上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衹有在彎角用INERTIA DRIFT了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見用他的拿手好戲INERTIA DRIFT
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越過哈利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進佔第五位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.03,0:22:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩屆冠軍的技術沒有退步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.83,0:22:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩屆冠軍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.87,0:22:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.84,0:22:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.14,0:22:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以給我快點退出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的眼中釘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.61,0:22:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺脫不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.88,0:22:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他沒衝著我而來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真是個討厭的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽剩下18個圈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.06,0:22:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領先的加賀和安尼·古利特相差兩秒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.86,0:22:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在後面追著他的是稍微落後在第四位的新條
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.66,0:22:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正和金色STIL在激烈比馴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.73,0:22:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.33,0:22:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:22:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使可以不斷使用DRIFT
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:23:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但車胎的磨損會很嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布林多·加賀的EXSSPERION正從後方接近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.18,0:23:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀快我一個圈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.09,0:23:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 你千萬不要踏進ZERO領域
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.12,0:23:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是一個正直的好傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.76,0:23:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不想讓你被那種
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像悲魔般的感覺所摧毀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.04,0:23:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓加賀過頭的話MISSIONEL也會超越我的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO領域來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.51,0:23:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要接觸ZERO領域
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是人類能踏進的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.32,0:23:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會原諒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.69,0:23:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.86,0:23:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能輸給那個領域
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是要戰勝它才回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.63,0:24:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.50,0:24:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ASURADA！AERO MODE!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.97,0:24:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 AERO MODE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.07,0:24:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升壓渦開動
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.48,0:24:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.62,0:24:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊卡洛斯之翼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.75,0:24:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升壓渦開動
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.83,0:24:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎會這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.01,0:24:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追種傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.31,0:24:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種傢伙是CYBER FORMULA的冠軍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.58,0:24:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追種傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.91,0:24:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麼事 隼人 開動升壓渦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.11,0:24:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推不動 推不動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.92,0:24:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升壓渦的梯縱桿推不動 美樹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.15,0:24:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.25,0:24:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.62,0:24:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ASURADA一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.96,0:24:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎會的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.36,0:25:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是完全推不動
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.26,0:25:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升壓渦正常
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.93,0:25:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人是你弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.63,0:25:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎會的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.73,0:25:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真的推不動
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.90,0:25:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推不動啊 美樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.17,0:25:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.24,0:25:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ASURADA慢下來 機件故障嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.34,0:25:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正陸續被後面的車越過
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.88,0:25:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生甚麼事 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.94,0:25:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機件正常 開動升壓渦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.18,0:25:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.87,0:25:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衹要有追求的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.07,0:25:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人便會變得堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.17,0:25:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論失敗多少次也會站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.48,0:25:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在光輝之中你會找到
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.75,0:26:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的東西存在
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.19,0:26:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算為了自己今天的失敗而哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.33,0:26:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍要找尋明天的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.60,0:26:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll GET VICTORY！VICTORY！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.64,0:26:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I Wlll BE WINNER！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.91,0:26:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會再一次得到勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.25,0:26:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll GET VICTORY！VICTORY！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.15,0:26:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I Wlll BE THE CHAMP！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.42,0:26:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的挑戰要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.86,0:26:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GET UP！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.29,0:27:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了我贏了風見啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.23,0:27:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂講！這有什麽好高興的，笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.47,0:27:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是總感到有些不對勁…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.63,0:27:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保捷賀爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.77,0:27:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為加速器有問題，而是事故的后遺症吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.44,0:27:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那中瞻前顧后的走法可不是我認識的風見
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.11,0:27:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回想起來吧，風見！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.75,0:27:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起你第一次參加大賽時
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.55,0:27:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種無所畏懼的挑戰者的心情！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.98,0:27:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高智能方程式 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.62,0:27:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ROUND 4.「天馬飛翔」
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.29,0:27:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在ZERO的領域里等著你！

